casebody.data:
In re Resignation of Friend. In re Friend.

[Cite as In re Resignation of Friend (1989), 47 Ohio St. 3d 612.]

(Nos. 89-1830 and 89-910 Submitted November 22, 1989 Decided December 6, 1989.)

The resignation of Ronald E. Friend as an attorney is accepted in case No. 89-1830. In view of Friend’s resignation from the practice of law, case No. 89-910, in which an indefinite suspension from the practice of law was ordered pursuant to Gov. Bar R. V(9)(a)(iii), is dismissed as moot.

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Holmes, Douglas, Wright, H. Brown and Resnick, JJ., concur.
